list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment:
Added test cases for the SignIn page. Modified the widget tree to allow a custom AuthService be common to the rest of the widgets, by using the newly added auth_info.dart with an InheritedWidget. This is for the testing process, and shouldn't affect the rest of the app (..?). Fixed a minor typo in a debug line in the auth.dart file.
May require the newly added auth_info.dart file to move package. Adds a dependency for Mockito v4.1.1 in the pubspec.yaml file.
